Package uk.ac.cf.milling.gui

Class GUIBuilder

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.cf.milling.gui.GUIBuilder
public class GUIBuilder extends Object
Initialises the GUI, builds its skeleton and triggers specialised builders
to create the panels that the user sees.
Author:
Theocharis Alexopoulos
